 1 - Backup Your Personal Data :-D
 
 2 - Install Needed Dev Packages (see configure.ac)
 
 3 - Install LibFmCore (See LibFmCore's README)
 
 4 - You Need A Recent Last Vala Release
 
 5 - Build With : make clean;make distclean;./autogen.sh && ./configure --enable-debug=yes --prefix=/usr && make
 
 6 - Try It In Debug Mode : "src/spanel -d"
 
 7 - Pray That It Will Work And That It Won't Screw Up Your Files :-P
 
 8 - Enjoy :)



